reviewText: Mix Benny Hill with Italian slap stick & a hint of the 3 Stooges with a tiny bit of nudity & you have this flick.  Unfortunately, I don't speak any Italian & my German is almost non-existent.  But I followed it along pretty easily.  Slightly better than average.  Again, if I could've understood it, it would've (fingers crossed) better.

SON PULICULAS QUE JAMAS PENSE QUE ENCONTRARA (EN SI POR LA ACTRIZ EDWIGE FENECH). Y ES EXCELENTE EL PAQUETE (AUNQUE NO TENGA SUBTITULOS EN ESPAOL, EL LENGUAJE SEA ITALIANO, PERO AH PASA)). GRACIAS
DIOS LOS SIGA BENDICIENDO MUCHOO!!!!!!!
